Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.51,0:00:03.78,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}《终空》前情提要\N{\fs40\b0}Previously on "Final Space"...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.82,0:00:06.15,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}银河一号上乱成一团\N{\fs40\b0}it's double trouble aboard the Galaxy One
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.18,0:00:08.75,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}因为总司令和无疆守卫\N{\fs40\b0}as the Lord Commander and the Infinity Guard
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.79,0:00:10.46,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}都把枪口对准了我们的船员\N{\fs40\b0}are both gunning for our crew.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.49,0:00:12.92,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}小卡多正在拼命地试图联系他的父亲...\N{\fs40\b0}Little Cato is desperately trying to contact his father...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.96,0:00:15.46,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}哦不！奎恩还正要解开\N{\fs40\b0}Oh, no!... and Quinn is about to unlock
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.49,0:00:17.33,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}威胁地球的巨大谜题\N{\fs40\b0}a huge mystery threatening Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.36,0:00:18.93,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}哦  双重的“不”\N{\fs40\b0}Oh, double no.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.96,0:00:21.50,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}光是想想这个  我裤子都绷紧了\N{\fs40\b0}My slacks are tightening just thinking about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.53,0:00:24.50,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}哦  三重的“不”\N{\fs40\b0}Oh, triple no.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.10,0:00:29.64,DIAT,,0,0,0,,{\be15}盖瑞  你还有5分钟氧气可用\N{\fs40\b0}Gary, you have 5 minutes of oxygen left.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.67,0:00:31.01,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}我之前活得很好\N{\fs40\b0}I lived a good life.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.04,0:00:33.75,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}中等偏上 有时稍微有点恶心\N{\fs40\b0}Medium to good / borderline crappy.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.78,0:00:36.95,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}我有次从袖口侧面看到过妹子的大波  棒极了\N{\fs40\b0}Saw some side boob once. That was cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.98,0:00:39.35,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}HUE  你见过“袖口侧面的大波”吗？\N{\fs40\b0}H.U.E., have you ever seen side boob?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.38,0:00:41.29,DIAT,,0,0,0,,{\be15}袖口侧面的大波？我没见过  盖瑞\N{\fs40\b0}Side boob? No, Gary.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.32,0:00:43.69,DIAT,,0,0,0,,{\be15}你说得越多  氧气也就...\N{\fs40\b0}The more you talk, the more oxygen you...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.72,0:00:47.09,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}你错过太多了  不过可能也没那么糟糕\N{\fs40\b0}You're missing out. I guess it wasn't all that bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.12,0:00:50.69,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}我收回刚刚那句话  我之前活的很好\N{\fs40\b0}In fact, I take it back. I lived a good one.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.06,0:00:54.80,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}当然了！这是...\N{\fs40\b0}Of course! This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.83,0:00:57.84,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}谢谢了！我的人生烂透了！\N{\fs40\b0}Thank you! My life sucks!
