Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.83,0:01:28.80,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}这就是盖瑞舰长\N{\fs40\b0}This is where Captain Gary wields
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.83,0:01:32.04,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}挥舞巨大的力量权杖的地方\N{\fs40\b0}the great giant scepter of power.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.07,0:01:35.01,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}你不是舰长  申请通信输出\N{\fs40\b0}You're not a Captain. Communication output requested.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.04,0:01:37.51,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}申请通信输出？真的吗？\N{\fs40\b0}Requesting a communications output, are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.54,0:01:40.21,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}你真的很知道怎么挑逗我\N{\fs40\b0}You really know how to press my buttons.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.24,0:01:43.43,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15} - 挑逗！   - 呃  那我就\N{\fs40\b0}- Press! - Ugh. Let me unpress your button
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.43,0:01:45.08,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}简单粗暴地告诉你\N{\fs40\b0}painfully short and clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.12,0:01:49.15,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}咱俩之间没有任何可能  绝对没有\N{\fs40\b0}It is never going to happen between us. Ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.25,0:01:52.72,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}这还真是又简单... 又粗暴！\N{\fs40\b0}That was painfully short... and clear!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.76,0:01:54.73,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}奎恩  为什么你都不肯给我一个机会？\N{\fs40\b0}Come on, Quinn. Why won't you give me a chance?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.76,0:01:57.06,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}你囚禁了无疆守卫的一员\N{\fs40\b0}You impersonated a member of the Infinity Guard
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.09,0:01:59.56,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}而且炸飞了92艘帝国巡飞舰\N{\fs40\b0}and blew up 92 Imperium Cruisers.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.60,0:02:01.60,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}你叫我怎么相信你\N{\fs40\b0}That doesn't inspire a lot of trust.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.63,0:02:03.53,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}那我猜  咱俩之间这份珍贵的情谊\N{\fs40\b0}Then I guess this precious thing we have between us
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.57,0:02:05.90,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}就算是断了吧  我很抱歉\N{\fs40\b0}is not gonna work out. I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.94,0:02:09.07,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15} - “你”竟然和“我”提出分手？   - 奎恩  我们之间结束了\N{\fs40\b0}- Did you just break up with me? - Quinn, it's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.11,0:02:11.41,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}我拔出了丘比特之箭  把它折断\N{\fs40\b0}I pulled the Cupid's arrow out, snapped it,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.44,0:02:13.21,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}又投进了分手的熊熊烈焰中\N{\fs40\b0}and threw it into the break-up flames.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.24,0:02:16.41,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}用它烤个棉花糖  继续你的生活吧\N{\fs40\b0}Toast a marshmallow and get on with your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.45,0:02:18.35,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}我没空和你玩这个\N{\fs40\b0}I don't have time for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.38,0:02:20.85,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}我需要进入无疆守卫网络的密码\N{\fs40\b0}I need to get the password to the Infinity Guard network.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.88,0:02:24.22,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}有人需要进入无疆守卫网络的密码吗？\N{\fs40\b0}Does someone need the password to the Infinity Guard network?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.25,0:02:26.39,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15} - 你怎么知道的？   - 我怎么知道的？\N{\fs40\b0}- How did you know? - How did I know?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.42,0:02:28.69,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15} - 我一直在听   - 真的？\N{\fs40\b0}- I'm always listening. - Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.73,0:02:30.59,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}你能别这样吗  马上停下行不行？\N{\fs40\b0}Can you stop that, like, immediately?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.63,0:02:33.83,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}我能吗？不  我不能\N{\fs40\b0}Can I? No, I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.60,0:02:37.40,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}就是这  HUE  放大\N{\fs40\b0}There it is, H.U.E. Zoom in.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.43,0:02:39.40,DIAT,,0,0,0,,{\be15}这个缺口有黑洞的特征\N{\fs40\b0}The breach has the characteristics
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.44,0:02:42.11,DIAT,,0,0,0,,{\be15}而且还在膨胀\N{\fs40\b0}of a black hole, and it's growing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.14,0:02:43.81,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}你和无疆守卫报告了这个\N{\fs40\b0}You told the Infinity Guard this
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.84,0:02:46.58,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}他们非但不听  还想把你抓起来？\N{\fs40\b0}and they didn't listen and they want to arrest you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.61,0:02:48.11,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}他们真是一群大坏蛋\N{\fs40\b0}They're total bad guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.15,0:02:50.28,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}无疆守卫的厨房里  散发出了\N{\fs40\b0}That smell coming from the Infinity Guard kitchen?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.31,0:02:52.98,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}一盘叫做“腐败大乱炖”的菜的味道！\N{\fs40\b0}A little dish I call Corruption Stew!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.02,0:02:55.12,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}无疆守卫一点都不腐败\N{\fs40\b0}The Infinity Guard is not corrupt.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.15,0:02:57.46,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}我懂了  你还在生我的气  因为我提出了分手\N{\fs40\b0}I get it. You're mad I broke up with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.49,0:03:00.62,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15} - 我的耐心快用完了   - 快用完了  你个妖女\N{\fs40\b0}- My patience is whittling away. - Whittle away, temptress.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.66,0:03:02.39,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}你的言语再也无法伤害我了\N{\fs40\b0}Your words can't hurt me anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.43,0:03:04.38,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}哇  好漂亮！这是啥？\N{\fs40\b0}Wow. How pretty! What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.42,0:03:09.43,DIAT,,0,0,0,,{\be15}等离子态的能量正从那颗行星射出  直接进入了缺口\N{\fs40\b0}Plasmic energy is firing from that planet directly into the breach.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.47,0:03:12.57,DIAT,,0,0,0,,{\be15}如果激光继续照下去  缺口将会扩大\N{\fs40\b0}If the laser continues, the breach will widen,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.60,0:03:15.14,DIAT,,0,0,0,,{\be15}地球将会被吸进去\N{\fs40\b0}and Earth will be consumed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.17,0:03:17.64,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}HUE  扫描一下那颗行星上的居住者\N{\fs40\b0}H.U.E., scan that planet for inhabitants.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.68,0:03:20.58,DIAT,,0,0,0,,{\be15}那是无疆守卫的前哨基地\N{\fs40\b0}That is an Infinity Guard Outpost.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.61,0:03:24.02,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}那味道不是汤  不是肉汤\N{\fs40\b0}It's not a soup. It's not a broth.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.05,0:03:27.18,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}哦！我知道了  那就是大乱炖的味道！\N{\fs40\b0}Oh! [Chuckles] I know. It's a stew!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.22,0:03:31.96,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15} - “腐败大乱炖”！   - 一定是有个可信的理由的\N{\fs40\b0}- Corruption stew! - There has to be a good explanation.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.99,0:03:34.43,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}我们过去  HUE  准备光折引擎\N{\fs40\b0}We're going. H.U.E., prime the lightfold engines.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.46,0:03:36.29,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}喔啊  喔啊  喔啊  喔啊  喔啊！\N{\fs40\b0}Whoa, whoa, whoa, whoa, whoa, whoa, whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.33,0:03:39.80,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}在我们分手的瞬间  控制权就已经回到舰长大人手里...\N{\fs40\b0}The moment we broke up, that right went back to el capitan...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.83,0:03:43.84,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15} - HUE  我们怎么能去那边？   - 需要舰长的巧计才能去那边...\N{\fs40\b0}- H.U.E., how do we get to the surface? - ...with a Captain's finesse.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.71,0:03:49.17,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}熄掉引擎  像个漂亮的飞鼠一样\N{\fs40\b0}Cutting the engines and gliding in
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.21,0:03:53.44,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}滑翔进去  这可不是个好主意！\N{\fs40\b0}like a glorious coasting stealth squirrel was a bad idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.23,0:04:15.55,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}好消息  如果这是正确的地方  我们已经到达目的地了\N{\fs40\b0}Good news. If this is the right place, we're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.17,0:04:19.88,DIAT,,0,0,0,,{\be15}正在评估损伤  导航装置阵列已下线\N{\fs40\b0}Assessing damage. The deflector array is offline.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.91,0:04:24.92,DIAT,,0,0,0,,{\be15}能量电池组已下线  烘焙房已下线\N{\fs40\b0}The power cells are offline. The bake shop is offline.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.95,0:04:27.18,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}等等！这艘飞船上还有烘焙房？！\N{\fs40\b0}Wait! There's a bake shop on this thing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.22,0:04:28.92,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}阿瓦卡多和我要下去侦查\N{\fs40\b0}Avocato and I will scout on foot.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.95,0:04:30.72,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}你们其他人留守阵地  修理飞船\N{\fs40\b0}The rest of you stay back and repair the ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.76,0:04:33.22,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}来吧  阿瓦卡多  咱们走  咋了？！\N{\fs40\b0}Come on, Avocato, let's go. What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.26,0:04:35.83,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}如果让我飞速吐露一下真心话\N{\fs40\b0}If I could pour a tall glass of truth-juice
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.86,0:04:39.70,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}奎恩... 我觉得你不信任我\N{\fs40\b0}for you real quick, Quinn... I am not feeling the trust.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.73,0:04:41.57,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}在这个世界上我只信任三个人\N{\fs40\b0}I only trust three people in this world...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.60,0:04:43.00,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}我的狗  我的姐姐\N{\fs40\b0}my dog, my sister,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.03,0:04:44.84,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}还有无疆守卫的每一个成员\N{\fs40\b0}and every single member of the Infinity Guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.87,0:04:48.57,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}你疯了  我的女士  无疆守卫正想把你捉拿归案\N{\fs40\b0}You're insane, my lady. The Infinity Guard tried to kidnap you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.61,0:04:50.54,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}他们还想接管银河一号\N{\fs40\b0}And they tried to take over the Galaxy One.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.57,0:04:52.08,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}而且狗不能算是人\N{\fs40\b0}And dogs aren't even people.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.11,0:04:54.08,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}我没理由相信你们之中的任何一个\N{\fs40\b0}I have no reason to trust any of you,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.11,0:04:57.52,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}所以我只和这个真的武装到牙齿的人出去\N{\fs40\b0}so I'm going with the guy literally covered in guns.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.28,0:05:02.29,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}KVN  好好修船  再有  不许碰我的任何东西\N{\fs40\b0}KVN, fix the ship. Also, don't touch any of my stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.32,0:05:05.26,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}也不许碰奎恩的  还有阿瓦卡多的  也不许碰饼干\N{\fs40\b0}Or Quinn's stuff. Or Avocato's. Or the cookies. Ju...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.29,0:05:07.96,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}就... 就别碰任何东西就成  尤其是各种按钮\N{\fs40\b0}Jus... Just don't touch anything. Specifically buttons.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.99,0:05:10.19,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}更尤其不许碰火焰喷射器\N{\fs40\b0}And especially flamethrowers.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.23,0:05:12.56,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}不过你得好好修船  修完就去死吧\N{\fs40\b0}But do fix the ship, and then die.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.60,0:05:15.27,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}听明白了吗？好的  来吧  月饼！\N{\fs40\b0}Okay? Okay. Okay, come on, Mooncake!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.30,0:05:17.27,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}\N{\fs40\b0}Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.27,0:05:20.27,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}呃\N{\fs40\b0}Ugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.15,0:05:30.45,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}好诶！\N{\fs40\b0}Hooray!
